types.name: Transaction
types.description: Transaction entities are created for each Ethereum transaction that contains an interaction within Livepeer contracts.

fields.name: id
fields.description: Ethereum transaction hash

fields.name: blockNumber
fields.description: Block transaction was mined in

fields.name: timestamp
fields.description: Timestamp for transaction

fields.name: gasUsed
fields.description: Amount of gas used in the transaction

fields.name: gasPrice
fields.description: Cost per unit of gas specified for the transaction

fields.name: from
fields.description: The sending party of the transaction

fields.name: to
fields.description: The receiving party of the transaction

fields.name: events
fields.description: The events emitted within this transaction

inputFields.name: _change_block
inputFields.description: Filter for the block changed event.

types.name: Transcoder
types.description: Perform transcoding work for the network. The transcoders with the most delegated stake are elected as active transcoders that process transcode jobs for the network.

fields.name: id
fields.description: Transcoder's ETH address

fields.name: activationRound
fields.description: Round in which the transcoder became active - 0 if inactive

fields.name: deactivationRound
fields.description: Round in which the transcoder will become inactive

fields.name: lastActiveStakeUpdateRound
fields.description: Round for which the stake was last updated while the transcoder is active

fields.name: active
fields.description: Whether or not the transcoder is active

fields.name: status
fields.description: Status of the transcoder

fields.name: lastRewardRound
fields.description: Last round that the transcoder called reward

fields.name: rewardCut
fields.description: % of block reward cut paid to transcoder by a delegator

fields.name: feeShare
fields.description: % of fees paid to delegators by transcoder

fields.name: pricePerSegment
fields.description: Price per segment for a stream

fields.name: pendingPricePerSegment
fields.description: Pending price per segment for next round if the transcoder is active

fields.name: pendingRewardCut
fields.description: Pending block reward cut for next round if the transcoder is active

fields.name: pendingFeeShare
fields.description: Pending fee share for next round if the transcoder is active

fields.name: totalStake
fields.description: Total tokens delegated toward a transcoder (including their own)

fields.name: totalVolumeETH
fields.description: Total fees generated by the transcoder in ETH (before distribution to delegators)

fields.name: totalVolumeUSD
fields.description: Total fees generated by the transcoder in USD (before distribution to delegators)

fields.name: pools
fields.description: Pools associated with the transcoder

fields.name: delegators
fields.description: Delegators bonded to the transcoder

fields.name: delegator
fields.description: Delegator that registered this transcoder

fields.name: serviceURI
fields.description: Service URI endpoint that can be used to send off-chain requests

types.name: TranscoderActivatedEvent
types.description: TranscoderActivatedEvent entities are created for every emitted TranscoderActivated event.

fields.name: id
fields.description: Ethereum transaction hash + event log index

fields.name: transaction
fields.description: Reference to the transaction the event was included in

fields.name: timestamp
fields.description: Timestamp of the transaction the event was included in

fields.name: round
fields.description: Reference to the round the event occured in

fields.name: delegate
fields.description: Reference to the delegate that will be active

fields.name: activationRound
fields.description: Future round in which the delegate will become active

inputFields.name: _change_block
inputFields.description: Filter for the block changed event.

fields.description: Combination of the transcoder address and the timestamp rounded to current day by dividing by 86400

fields.name: date
fields.description: The date beginning at 12:00am UTC

fields.name: volumeETH

fields.name: volumeUSD
fields.description: Fees generated this day in USD

fields.name: transcoder
fields.description: Transcoder associated with the day

inputFields.name: _change_block
inputFields.description: Filter for the block changed event.
